The Leaking Underground Storage Tank (L.U.S.T.) tax of 0.1 cents per gallon which is assessed on fuel dispensed from underground tanks and used to pay for remedial actions required to address leaks from such tanks.
Substance Superfund Tax on imports, exports, and production of crude oil and petroleum products, which is used to pay for clean up and related costs resulting from oil spills.
